snippet.title: SD Gundam Battle Alliance - Announcement Trailer - Coming 2022
snippet.description:
Join a Battle Alliance to Correct a False World in SD Gundam Battle Alliance!

#SDGundamBA is coming in 2022 for Nintendo Switch, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Steam and PC! 

Follow Bandai Namco Entertainment: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bandainamcous
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/bandainamcous
